been a significant
dip in their output in terms of
their propaganda.

28:54.600 --> 28:57.836 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They're putting out less videos,
less images,
et cetera.

28:57.869 --> 29:04.009 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I wouldn't be quick to
declare victory
of any kind. This is a group
that has shown

29:04.042 --> 29:08.814 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
