Germany that
was meant to be against the
Berlin Airport

29:20.726 --> 29:25.664 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
possibly, and that, according to
the officials
I have spoken to, could have
looked as bad

29:25.697 --> 29:28.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
