saw in March
of this year.

29:28.100 --> 29:31.737 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Peter Neumann,
is there
anything you would add to that
about how ISIS

29:31.770 --> 29:33.572 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
