29:33.605 --> 29:35.240 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
PETER NEUMANN, Director,
International Center
for the Study of Radicalization,
King's College:

29:35.273 --> 29:39.678 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Right now, there are still an
estimated 10,000
foreign fighters in ISIS
territory.

29:39.711 --> 29:45.651 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
