home countries.
Others will try to go to other
battlefronts.

29:50.889 --> 29:57.129 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So I think the story of ISIS is
not over once
ISIS is defeated in Syria and
Iraq.

29:57.162 --> 30:01.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Peter, just
staying with
