you have found?

30:11.943 --> 30:17.482 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PETER NEUMANN: So, if you speak
to European
security agencies, they will
tell you that,

30:17.516 --> 30:22.654 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
